2. Flower:zinnia is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Nationality:british##1
4. Flower:bellflower is on the left of Nationality:british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Flower         | balloon-flower | bellflower | marigold | zinnia |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

